title: Candy Cane Garden - Fish [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~~
description:
Candy Cane Garden - Fish ? (1996)

MP3 - 320kbs

The First Studio Album from the Swedish Rock Band, Two weeks before they enter the Studio they decided to change the Vocalist from Jonas Hediget (Dragonland, Destiny) To Jonas Udd (BULT), so the new singer didnt know any of the songs realy before the recording of this album, but they pulled it of anyway...

The results were 4 radio hits "Milkshop", "Feathered Cloud", "Wishes", "Mudslide"
